---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
    title="Terms and Conditions - DropX" 
    description="Read the terms and conditions for using DropX. By using our peer-to-peer file sharing platform, you agree to these rules and guidelines for secure and responsible file transfer."
>
    <div class="container py-24 md:py-32">
        <div class="max-w-[800px] mx-auto prose dark:prose-invert">
            <h1 class="text-display-md md:text-display-xl mb-8 text-ink">Terms and Conditions</h1>
            
            <p class="text-body-md text-body mb-8">
                Last updated: May 31, 2026
            </p>

            <section class="mb-12">
                <h2 class="text-display-sm mb-4 text-ink">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
                <p class="text-body-md text-body mb-4">
                    By accessing and using DropX (the "Service"), you agree to be bound by these Terms and Conditions. If you do not agree to these terms, please do not use the Service.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-12">
                <h2 class="text-display-sm mb-4 text-ink">2. Description of Service</h2>
                <p class="text-body-md text-body mb-4">
                    DropX provides a <strong>peer-to-peer file sharing</strong> platform that allows users to transfer files directly between browsers. The Service is provided "as is" and we are not responsible for the content of the files transferred.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-12">
                <h2 class="text-display-sm mb-4 text-ink">3. User Responsibilities</h2>
                <p class="text-body-md text-body mb-4">
                    When using our <strong>file sharing service</strong>, you agree to:
                </p>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-body-md text-body space-y-2">
                    <li>Only transfer files that you have the right to share.</li>
                    <li>Not use the Service for any illegal activities, including the distribution of malware or copyrighted material without permission.</li>
                    <li>Not attempt to disrupt or interfere with the Service's operation.</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-12">
                <h2 class="text-display-sm mb-4 text-ink">4. Peer-to-Peer Nature</h2>
                <p class="text-body-md text-body mb-4">
                    You acknowledge that DropX is a <strong>decentralized file sharing</strong> tool. We do not store, monitor, or have access to any files you transfer. You are solely responsible for the security of your connections and the files you choose to share.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-12">
                <h2 class="text-display-sm mb-4 text-ink">5. Intellectual Property</h2>
                <p class="text-body-md text-body mb-4">
                    The Service and its original content, features, and functionality are and will remain the exclusive property of DropX. You retain all ownership rights to the files you transfer.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-12">
                <h2 class="text-display-sm mb-4 text-ink">6. Limitation of Liability</h2>
                <p class="text-body-md text-body mb-4">
                    In no event shall DropX be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages, including without limitation, loss of profits, data, use, goodwill, or other intangible losses, resulting from your use of the Service.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-12">
                <h2 class="text-display-sm mb-4 text-ink">7. Termination</h2>
                <p class="text-body-md text-body mb-4">
                    We reserve the right to terminate or suspend access to our Service immediately, without prior notice or liability, for any reason whatsoever, including without limitation if you breach the Terms.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-12">
                <h2 class="text-display-sm mb-4 text-ink">8. Contact Us</h2>
                <p class="text-body-md text-body mb-4">
                    If you have any questions about these Terms, please contact us at <a href="mailto:terms@dropx.top" class="text-primary hover:underline">terms@dropx.top</a>.
                </p>
            </section>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>
